The transition probabilities between these states are given by the following matrix:

P = 
[0.9 0.1 0   0   0;
 0   0.8 0.2 0   0;
 0   0   0.7 0.3 0;
 0   0   0   0.6 0.4;
 0   0   0   0   1]

where P(i, j) is the probability of moving from state i to state j in one time step. 

1) What is the probability that the young immigrant will reach the "Citizenship granted" state starting from the "Initial application" state?

2) If the young immigrant is currently in the "Background check" state, what is the expected number of steps until they reach the "Citizenship granted" state?
